keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

unmap d
unmap D
unmap u
unmap J
unmap K
unmap e
unmap E
unmap x
unmap X
unmap b
unmap B

map J scrollPageDown
map K scrollPageUp
map e Vomnibar.activateEditUrl
map E Vomnibar.activateEditUrlInNewTab
map d removeTab
map D restoreTab
map <a-h> previousTab
map <a-l> nextTab
map b goBack
map B goForward
